{"title":"【079】CSS填充和宽高","slug":"hell0-world25","date":"2022-10-19T13:20:27.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:19:33.326Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world25.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                padding        内边距","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>padding</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"padding-style.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <h1>内边距</h1>\n    <span id=\"more\"></span>\n    <div>\n    元素内容周围产生空间，用padding顺序为上右下左。lenth以px,pt,cm等为单位指定边距；以父元素宽度的百分比指定边距。<br><br>\n    元素具有指定宽度，加在上面的填充会加入总宽度。<br><br>\n    width,height属性不包含内填充，边框和外边距的。<br><br>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}